  "detailed_description": "<ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Strategy : survive attacks for each portals active period and use portals cool down period for exploring and dig for materials and crafting and setup defenses an paths.. more over you should take care of robot's battery and manage power wisely..<br></li><li>Monk's Shop: When the robot enters Monks ceramic zone you can access the shop, sell, buy items and achieve requests..<br></li><li>Enemies & Allies: From multiple worlds..<br></li><li>Weapons: There are many sorts of defense like Weapon facility can be mounted with a weapon, shield and  class-mod modules..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373230/extras/137fd46dee60f9f6217f6b658050da8d.poster.avif?t=1614287745\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373230/extras/137fd46dee60f9f6217f6b658050da8d.webm?t=1614287745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Traps and barrels..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373230/extras/9c8bf634384bab22963ece48e13f1917.poster.avif?t=1614287745\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373230/extras/9c8bf634384bab22963ece48e13f1917.webm?t=1614287745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>Robot built in turret..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373230/extras/7d5a3f539878dd0ce7a9782d128a5fc7.poster.avif?t=1614287745\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373230/extras/7d5a3f539878dd0ce7a9782d128a5fc7.webm?t=1614287745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br></li><li>Build factories: generator facility to produce power batteries, weapon factory, engineering factory, elemental factory, class-mod factory, body-parts factory..<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373230/extras/dc6a6966a04cc5d03593ec5ac3fa9aa1.poster.avif?t=1614287745\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1373230/extras/dc6a6966a04cc5d03593ec5ac3fa9aa1.webm?t=1614287745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br></li><li>Other Facilities: Walls, Research station for process researches.. and more..<br></li><li>World: you can create unlimited auto generated infinite worlds, with zones, each zone have unique tiles..</li></ul>",
